Fields.Name: AmountToBeLoaded
Fields.Description:
Amount to be credited/Offer charge (via API) - Add 00 to value
Amount to Transfer(Mobile Transfer) - no need to add 00

Fields.Name: Discount
Fields.Description: Convert Percentage to Decimal Form (Only for scenarios that uses Retailer MIN for Transaction)

Fields.Name: TestCaseID
Fields.Description: Unique Test Case ID for TCs Identification

Fields.Name: SupplementaryOffering
Fields.Description: Supplementary Offering ID to be credited/ already credited

Fields.Name: FreeUnitTypeID
Fields.Description: Unique Free Unit Type ID for adjustment of wallet

Fields.Name: MeasurementUnit
Fields.Description: Identifier for Voice Usage - Minutes, Seconds

Fields.Name: AdjustmentType
Fields.Description: Adjustment Type of Airtime/Free Unit - Add, Deduct

Fields.Name: WelcomePackage
Fields.Description: Welcome Package to be credited/already credited

Entities.Description: AD EVC and MM Regression Testing

Fields.Name: DomainType
Fields.Description: For MINs that need to be validated in OCS website

Fields.Name: SupplementaryOfferingName
Fields.Description: Input Supplementary Offering Name as displayed or will be displayed in OCS

Entities.Name: ADSIMRegistration
Entities.Description: Test Data Service for SIM Registration Testing

Fields.Name: TypeofRegistration
Fields.Description:
1 - I'm registering a newly bought SIM
2 - I'm registering a newly bought SIM for a Minor
3 - I'm registering an old SIM for a Minor
4 - I'm registering my old SIM

Fields.Name: IDCard
Fields.Description:
1 - Philippine Identification
2 - Driver's License
3 - UMID
4 - TIN
5 - Philippines Passport
6 - Postal ID
7 - Voter's ID
8 - SSS
9 - PRC ID
10 - PhilHealth ID
11 - BIR ID
12 - Firearm's License to Own and Possess ID
13 - GSIS
14 - Integrated Bar of the Philippines ID
15 - NBI Clearance
16 - Other valid ID
17 - OWWA ID
18 - PWD Card
19 - Police Clearance
20 - Senior Citizen's Card

Entities.Name: OCSUIAutomation
Entities.Description: Test Data Service for OCS UI Automation Testing

Fields.Name: TestEnvironment
Fields.Description: Environment where the testing must be done (TB1/TB2)

Fields.Name: ChangeSubInfo
Fields.Description: Decision whether to change subinfo or not. (True/False)

Fields.Name: ActivateMIN
Fields.Description: Decision whether to activate subscriber MIN. (True/False)

Fields.Name: PrimaryOfferingID
Fields.Description: Subscriber MIN's Primary Offering ID Upon Registration

Fields.Name: SupplementaryOfferingID
Fields.Description: Subscriber MIN's supplementary offering ID upon availing load offers.

Fields.Name: LoadAmount
Fields.Description: Amount to be loaded to the subscriber MIN.

Fields.Name: OfferSubscription
Fields.Description: Decision whether MIN should avail load offer or not. (True/False)

Fields.Name: TestExecutionStatus
Fields.Description: Identifies whether data must be tested or not. If test data is to be tested, put "For Testing", otherwise put "Do not test."

Entities.Description: Contains Automation Cloud users and groups that have ever had roles assigned, or accessed Data Service
